snippet: Branislav Milinkovic, the Serbian ambassador to NATO, was a respected diplomat who had been an opposition activist during the rule of Slobodan Milosevic.
abstract: Branislav Milinkovic, Serbian ambassador to NATO, jumps to his death from multistory parking garage at Brussels airport; Serbian officials say motive is not known.
lead_paragraph: Branislav Milinkovic, the Serbian ambassador to NATO, was a respected diplomat who had been an opposition activist during the rule of Slobodan Milosevic.

headline.seo: Serbian Ambassador to NATO Is Said to Commit Suicide
headline.main: Serbia Envoy Said to Jump to His Death
